medicine_reminder_project/
│
├── main.py                  # CLI Menu App
├── gui_app.py               # GUI-based Reminder App
├── chatbot.py               # Rule-based chatbot (no API)
├── ocr_reader.py            # OCR using pytesseract
├── medicine.py              # Core medicine functions (add, read, check expiry, etc.)
├── requirements.txt         # Python dependencies
├── README.md                # Project overview and how to run
├── storage_large.csv        # Data file (you can include an empty one)
└── sample_prescription.jpg  # (Optional) Demo image for OCR
